# Browser Bookmarks (`touch-browser-bookmarks`)

## When to Use
- Keep frequently used links and recent visits in one place.

## Trigger
- Feature ID: `browser.bookmarks`
- Commands: `bookmark / bookmarks / 收藏 / 网址`

## Core Capabilities
- 浏览器收藏：收藏网址、最近访问、快速打开
- Supported platforms: `win32, darwin, linux`

## Config & Data
- Config/data files: `bookmarks.json`, `recent-urls.json`
- Plugin directory: `plugins/touch-browser-bookmarks`

## Permissions
- Optional: `clipboard.write`

## Quick Start
1. In CoreBox, type `bookmark`.
2. Press Enter on the action you need.
3. Grant permissions when prompted.
